OL,3,C18-year-old man arrested as car
OL,4,Ccrashes into busy Broadstairs pub
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a car
OL,7,Fsmashed into a popular Broadstairs pub
OL,8,Fin the early hours of Saturday morning.
OL,10,FKent Police were called to Albion Road
OL,11,Fat 1.56am on 4 April after reports
OL,12,Fthat a vehicle had collided with The
OL,13,FDolphin Inn, causing significant
OL,14,Fdamage to the building.
OL,16,FEmergency services, including officers
OL,17,Fand paramedics, attended the scene.
OL,18,FMinor injuries were reported, with
OL,19,Fthose affected treated at the scene.
