OL,3,C18-year-old man arrested as car
OL,4,Ccrashes into busy Broadstairs pub
OL,6,FShocking footage shared online shows
OL,7,Fthe moment the car struck the pub,
OL,8,Fprompting nearby residents to rush
OL,9,Foutside in concern. The incident
OL,10,Fcaused chaos on the street, though no
OL,11,Fserious injuries have been confirmed.
OL,13,FAn 18yearold man has been arrested
OL,14,Fand remains in custody as detectives
OL,15,Finvestigate.
OL,17,FOfficers are appealing for witnesses,
OL,18,Fdashcam, or mobile phone footage to
OL,19,Fassist with enquiries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
