OL,3,C18-year-old man arrested as car
OL,4,Ccrashes into busy Broadstairs pub
OL,6,FThe pub has reopened following the
OL,7,Fincident, in a statement posted on
OL,8,FFacebook they said:
OL,10,F"We want to reassure everyone that we
OL,11,Fare open as normal after undergoing
OL,12,Frepairs. Thank you (customers) so much
OL,13,Ffor all the support and kindness we've
OL,14,Freceived."
